# "Okay deploy" ŌĆö full BimRoss release pass

When Grant says **okay deploy**, **deploy everything**, or clearly means **push + release + verify rollout** (multi-repo, not a one-line fix in a single file), execute this protocol.

## Authorization

This is an **explicit release / deploy** request. **Pushing `v*` tags** for **`cursor-rules`** (and **`employee-factory`** when its code changed) is **in scope** for this turnŌĆösee the exception note in **`bimross-git-dev-and-releases.mdc`**.

## Default scope

| Repo | Typical action |
|------|----------------|
| **`cursor-rules`** | `master` pushed; then **next semver `v*`** tag ŌåÆ **`geeemoney/cursor-rules`** image + GitOps updates **`cursor-rules` init** lines in **`rancher-admin`** `admin/apps/employee-factory/{alex,tim,ross}-deployment.yaml`. |
